campaigns.title: Humankindness The Animal Dilemma Documentary Film
campaigns.desc: Help us turn the inspiring story of Humankindness - The Animal Dilemma into a must-see documentary.
campaigns.content:
In a culture disconnected, what connects everyone?

LOVE!

In a new inspiring documentary Humankindness - The Animal Dilemma, join Anja and Matej, a crazy couple on a mission to change the world for the voiceless, one another, and the planet.

Discover how being kind to animals can save us all!

Anja is a nurse from Switzerland and Matej is a content creator from Slovenia who both fell in love at an animal rights workshop.

The film follows their inspiring mission to have a completely vegan wedding while carrying out animal rights events and discovering the global dilemma so many people still face when their love for animals is compromised when we sit at a table to eat.

The film features exclusive interviews with various vegan and non-vegan experts, farmers, influencers, vegan celebrities, and ordinary people who love animals and face this dilemma on a daily basis.

Anja and Matej take audiences on their eye-opening journey to explore what solutions exist now and in the future on how we use our combined Humankindness to live in a better world for everyone on the planet.

Our initial FLEXIBLE GOAL is €15,000 

However, our ULTIMATE STRETCH GOAL for the campaign is €42,000

Now we need your help in getting the film and its story and message to the world.

And, if you love animals as much as we do, then we wholeheartedly welcome you to our crowdfunding campaign to become one of our invaluable backers to support us in completing the film.

50% of the film is already shot and the purpose of our Indiegogo crowdfunding campaign is to raise the remaining 50% of the necessary funds to help us complete the next stage of the production with your invaluable support.

Making a documentary film is a complicated endeavor. It is expensive too. We have a dedicated team of people who are ready and willing to help us complete the film in style.


We also have to outsource help and film interviews in many different locations around the world and this is why your support is so vital at this stage.

We’re so excited to invite as many awesome animal lovers to be part of this unique movie.

Please check out a breakdown of where the funds raised will be going below.


 

The film will feature exclusive interviews with a selection of respected vegan and non-vegan experts from all over the world including the following;
